{"tid":1529951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果一早講定去邊會俾人捕,咁當日/前一日先講去邊可唔可行?","createTime":"2019-09-01T23:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T02:19:05.000Z","uid":37350,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ebcf54a96bb7e12252caa21288a3e43fd131de07","tid":1529951,"uid":37350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T23:53:00.000Z","msg":"軍政府已經做壞咗個頭令香港人冇示威集會自由,係唔撚係都拉非法集結<br />\n申請不反對都只係通知佢<br />\n佢做壞個頭咁我地唔使通知佢啦<br />\n有冇人諗到有咩方法可以當日有效正確地傳俾人聽去邊<br />\n反正會出嚟都準備好星期六日會出嚟<br />\n9.2罷完工突然話全世界去機場等等<br />\n佢邊阻得切我地入去<br />\n大家點睇?<br />\nset個poll投票去邊,當日先公開可唔可行<br />\n但係咁做可能會變到有大台<br />\n有乜諗頭"},{"pid":"87359760eb1968a3d86232550da5914a33ad100c","tid":1529951,"uid":37350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T23:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d44cfe1431eff7a4e62ffbbfb38069a64a62592","tid":1529951,"uid":37350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T23:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb5f901250433ecdbf2a2e7e61aac1a80797941","tid":1529951,"uid":28279,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T23:55:02.000Z","msg":"會集唔夠人，三兩個警察就搞掂你"},{"pid":"29a8140667c119881d61934b7299eb49e268ce06","tid":1529951,"uid":37350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T23:55:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e5cbef95ba39a03d51178c9318e203529a72e2a","tid":1529951,"uid":37350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"feb5f901250433ecdbf2a2e7e61aac1a80797941","tid":1529951,"uid":28279,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T23:55:02.000Z","msg":"會集唔夠人，三兩個警察就搞掂你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T23:57:38.000Z","msg":"反正會出嚟都準備好星期六日會出嚟<br />\n咪又係次次都係邊到開始多人<br />\n你10,11am講去邊<br />\n出門口食完個飯出到嚟啱啱好<br />\n香港人出嚟幾可要坐成兩個鐘以上"},{"pid":"fba8e82f09b15c1b26bb458db984d0